es/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"1abf809d68eeed6010ac385d4aa977e24375100b","tid":241681,"uid":105665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:01:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拿 7仔呢就淨係返星期六日都得既  唔撚搵工上網乞你真係以為有人會俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n我臨急臨忙先醒起母親節要感激媽媽我係懶係偽孝 大家屌得我好岩 以為放D垃圾上黎賣 就可以掩飾自己想乞錢..對唔住各位 我真係好撚低賤"},{"pid":"ef11a2454b24bf741ce0e4640b429da5a155434d","tid":241681,"uid":35774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:02:34.000Z","msg":"乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442cba4120aec157ba1c503197e46a58b82c90dd","tid":241681,"uid":7744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:05:06.000Z","msg":"死出去返part time啦  乞衣仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e25a2d6e720d8e1475f4bbfd0b229a935c6ac3","tid":241681,"uid":105665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:05:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你幫佢拖地咪得lor<br />\n做乜鳩</blockquote><br />\n真係好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗錢就做到既野走上黎乞<br />\n第時結婚生仔洗唔洗幫樓主屌大個老婆幫佢老母添孫</blockquote><br />\n我會長大 唔會再求人 多謝巴打把口咁賤催促我快點去長大改善自己有事就求人的錯誤態度!"},{"pid":"ef79814487d0e4468d459dac8b7cdbecf7a10127","tid":241681,"uid":8498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:09:57.000Z","msg":"父親節再post過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da15bde68a53812238ace6b94e8e63808aa510a","tid":241681,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:15:52.000Z","msg":"樓主心智好細路哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打一大篇野講到自己走投無路上黎籌旗<br />\n以為會搏到大家同情 <br />\n就算巴打唔捐錢都會大讚自己孝順<br />\n點知原來平時有錢買av冇錢孝敬老媽子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即刻寫張卡買札花影相放上黎補鑊<br />\n故意影埋張卡內容打算令班巴打刮目相看，怪錯你依個孝順仔<br />\n又即刻認自己係偽孝係不孝子<br />\n想拎返個尾彩<br />\n查實樓主一直最想人讚你孝順呀孝感動天呀然後幾百正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}